rows.label: qst200918_msg001
rows.name: We're back!

rows.label: qst200918_msg002
rows.name: Ah, so you are!

rows.label: qst200918_msg003
rows.name:
Looks like we've got everything
we need now to open the shop
again. Thank you!

rows.label: qst200918_msg004
rows.name: Aww, it was nothing.

rows.label: qst200918_msg005
rows.name:
It's all worthwhile as
long as I can put a smile
back on people's faces!

rows.label: qst200918_msg006
rows.name: You're a good lass, you know that?

rows.label: qst200918_msg016
rows.name:
What do you say to a couple
more loaves of freshly-baked
Lucky Dawn Bread as thanks?

rows.label: qst200918_msg017
rows.name: Whoa, really?!

rows.label: qst200918_msg018
rows.name:
Oh, that would be amazing!
I'm feeling so blessed!

rows.label: qst200918_msg019
rows.name:
Heh, someone's pleased! That
smile of yours is catching!

rows.label: qst200918_msg007
rows.name: Ehehe...

rows.label: qst200918_msg008
rows.name: Mo... Should all just be careful.

rows.label: qst200918_msg009
rows.name:
Getting involved with Kasane
nothing but trouble.

rows.label: qst200918_msg010
rows.name:
Need to put her on
blacklist of trade guild!

rows.label: qst200918_msg011
qst200918_msg012
rows.name: Mo-mo... Whose fault you think...

rows.label: qst200918_msg013
rows.name:
If there's anything I can do
to help, please tell me!

rows.label: qst200918_msg014
rows.name:
Meeeeeh... How can be angry at someone
when they so kind and innocent?

rows.label: qst200918_msg015
rows.name:
If only Kasane not bringer
of bad luck, would be whole
different story...

rows.label: qst200918_msg020
rows.name:
Huh? I don't bring bad luck!
There's no way that'd happen!

rows.label: qst200918_msg021
rows.name:
Seconded. I don't see how such
a sweet little girl could ever
bring misfortune on anyone.

rows.label: qst200918_msg022
rows.name: Mo-mo-moooo...

rows.label: qst200918_msg023
rows.name: Kupon lost for words...

rows.label: qst200918_msg101
rows.name:
Well, what does my Driver
have to say about this? Did
we bring happiness or not?

rows.label: qst200918_msg102
rows.name:
Yeah, I think so. I think you've
brightened everyone's days a little.

rows.label: qst200918_msg103
rows.name:
Though I can't help but notice
a lot of unlucky things
happened along the way...

rows.label: qst200918_msg104
rows.name:
Yeah, I guess so. Maybe
just a tiny bit happier.

rows.label: qst200918_msg105
rows.name:
Though some pretty terrible things
did happen along the way...

rows.label: qst200918_msg106
rows.name:
I would say so. You've taken
great pains to bring happiness
to people in need.

rows.label: qst200918_msg107
rows.name:
Though I must admit, your efforts
were punctuated by a series of
unfortunate coincidences...

rows.label: qst200918_msg108
rows.name:
Yeah, absolutely. I think you've
done a smashing job of helping out.

rows.label: qst200918_msg109
rows.name:
But now that you mention it, we've had
so many disasters in such a short time,
it seems more than coincidence.

rows.label: qst200918_msg110
rows.name:
I suppose you're right...
I wonder if it's because
my powers are incomplete?

rows.label: qst200918_msg111
rows.name: Uh, yeah...that must be it...

rows.label: qst200918_msg112
rows.name: Uhh, yeah...must be...

rows.label: qst200918_msg113
rows.name: Er...perhaps...

rows.label: qst200918_msg114
rows.name: Hmm...I dunno...

rows.label: qst200918_msg115
rows.name:
I'll try hard, really I will!
I just want to bring people
happiness, that's all!

rows.label: qst200918_msg116
rows.name:
I understand. We're
counting on you, Kasane!

rows.label: qst200918_msg117
rows.name:
Yeah, I know. Well, we're
counting on you, Kasane!

rows.label: qst200918_msg118
rows.name:
Well said, Kasane. I look forward
to seeing your progress!

rows.label: qst200918_msg119
rows.name:
I hear you. Well, we're
counting on you, Kasane,
so don't you forget it!
